values: ...it was WEIRD! we were like going on this school trip thingy and then there were a bunch of Jedi's up on this hill 'cause we thought it was going to be a jedi tournament but then general griveous told everyone to leave and so it was only me and obi-wan left. i was scared to death like "omg, he has 8 arms...he could kill us!!!!" but then this hawk comes up and general griveous  goes "Obi-wan, do you remember this bird?" Obi-wan (which i think kept changing to jenn or something) said "yes.." (GG) "Lets see if he comes back to you...." *the bird flies and falls onto the roof. GG laughs* so we go on with this and he just keeps talking and i'm scared to death. at one point a dirt bike race went through where we were so we had to hide for a minute. when we came back out i raised my hand then said "Um...General Grevious...I'm feeling sick...can I go home?" and he goes "no" then "phase one" was over (which was just talking about animals) and we got to leave...obi-wan was like "Anakin, i'm sorry you had to go through that" and i was all scared and crap...that's all i remember.

...so here goes a post!!! \
